[327.815, "o", "\u001b[2m  # over the limit, the agent does not pay. it retried notifying the owner three times,\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[2m  # reports it could not reach them, and holds the spend. agent A still has all 100 LEZ.\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[1;32m  ✓ above the limit: notified, retried, reported, never executed\u001b[0m\r\n"]
